---
import globe from "../images/binary-globe.svg";
---

<main>
    <div>
        <h1>Web Developer</h1>
        <img
            src={globe}
            width="260px"
            height="260px"
            alt="Globe Image In Binary Format"
            class="filter mobile"
        />
        <p>
            Welcome to my website. My name is Przemysław Niewoliński. I am a
            junior web developer. I like programming in general, but I am most
            interested in the anything related to web technologies - websites,
            web applications & cloud. There is something inherently fascinating
            about code being live, available on the internet and potentially
            used by millions at the same time. I like simplicity and when it
            comes to code, I consider myself a minimalist - ship as little code
            as possible with clean architecture in mind. Check out my <a
                href="#projects">projects</a
            > or <a href="#technologies">technologies</a> that i use.
        </p>
        <nav>
            <a class="buttonLink" href="https://github.com/niewolinsky"
                >GitHub</a
            >
            <a class="buttonLink" href="https://codewars.com/users/Niewolinsky"
                >CodeWars</a
            >
            <a
                class="buttonLink"
                href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/przemys%C5%82aw-niewoli%C5%84ski-847521245/"
                >LinkedIn</a
            >
        </nav>
    </div>
    <img
        src={globe}
        width="340px"
        height="340px"
        alt="Globe Image In Binary Format"
        class="filter desktop"
    />
</main>
<style>
    img.desktop {
        margin-left: 80px;
    }
    img.mobile {
        display: none;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
    img.filter {
        filter: invert(var(--inversion-power));
    }

    nav {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        column-gap: 12px;
    }

    main {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: justify;
    }

    a {
        text-decoration: underline;
        color: var(--accent-color);
    }

    .buttonLink {
        border: 1px solid var(--text-color);
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        color: var(--text-color);
        background-color: var(--background-color);
        border-style: solid;
        cursor: pointer;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
    .buttonLink:hover {
        color: var(--background-color);
        border: 1px solid var(--text-color);
        background-color: var(--accent-color);
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
        main {
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        nav {
            justify-content: space-evenly;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        img.mobile {
            display: block;
        }

        img.desktop {
            display: none;
        }
    }
</style>
